latestPosts.alt: A reminder to keep your faith and kindness alive

childPosts.alt: A reminder to keep your faith and kindness alive
Trust the process, every step is leading to something greater
Never underestimate the power of little kindness- a smile, a kind word or a helping hand
Life isn’t supposed to be easy, it’s supposed to be worth it
You are not defined by other peoples limited views of you
you have the power to create positive change, no matter where you are
People see the world only as much as they are open to it
It’s okay to say no and prioritize your wellbeing
The more you nurture your own soul, the more positivity you can spread around you
Don’t let anyone else’s idea of you change the way you see the world
Send this to someone who needs to hear it. Because sometimes we just need to hear it.
